{"tid":1164414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要讓香港成為歷史","createTime":"2019-05-21T05:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T15:54:20.000Z","uid":165234,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f049b12a7c129074ca46da04c486664a71721b30","tid":1164414,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/oca_TrMGIBM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Foca_TrMGIBM&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=5e20507b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oca_TrMGIBM</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">我們被選中<br />\n為世界服務<br />\n<br />\n但是政治<br />\n逼迫我們選擇<br />\n<br />\n這座城市<br />\n孤立無援<br />\n<br />\n有人殊死一搏<br />\n嘗試拯救我們<br />\n<br />\n沒有任何幫助<br />\n這裏窮途末路<br />\n<br />\n城市被放棄了<br />\n但更重要的是<br />\n人性也被放棄了<br />\n<br />\n不要讓香港成為歷史</div>"},{"pid":"88d70723e3a674bc41f29bf4d0e4b7e764a83d60","tid":1164414,"uid":165234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:21:51.000Z","msg":"想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65c578aeee13cffd45418444bcc8ebc9afd19fe","tid":1164414,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49be2bb205e83184e300665b249aaf67c30effa","tid":1164414,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:19:26.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"b40cc232e1ba04b4af0145c2652e700cb7dcee2f","tid":1164414,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/